headline: Principal Financial (PFG) Q1 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Principal Financial (PFG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.16% and 0.98%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
